Today is International Polar Bear day. I took this shot during a magical sunset in Churchill, Manitoba while obviously observing this mother and two cubbies. I feel fortunate that I was not only able share this moment with one of my best friends and some new ones while out with @discover_churchill , but also to spend a week learning about this beautiful animal and it’s human induced struggle in the arctic. #polarbears #churchill #canada #manitoba #wildlife #sonyalpha #a7r #photography #wildlifephotography #animals #polarbears #svalbard

Got to sing one of my favorite songs with my hero. Never in a million years could I have dreamt this one up! 

Last night’s hometown show at The Belasco in Los Angeles was truly a night to remember. We’re so grateful to all of our hometown fans, family, and friends in attendance, but especially to Chris Robinson for jumping on stage with us. The Black Crowes inspired so much of my musical journey to even think we’d share the stage with such an icon and perform an AC/DC song together was beyond my wildest dreams. But if you never try you’ll never know, so in the words of Bon Scott “Take your chance, while you still got the choice…” - Marc LaBelle
@theblackcrowes @acdc @dirtyhoneyband 

📸 by @jakehicks
